\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The specificity of CT positioning is a topic of debate, though studies have
 suggested conservation of CT positioning through evolution 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Tanabe2002"

\end_inset

 and shown tissue specificity in chromosome pairing 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
